Name: EbookLib
Version: 0.17.1
Summary: Ebook library which can handle EPUB2/EPUB3 and Kindle format
Home-page: https://github.com/aerkalov/ebooklib
Author: Aleksandar Erkalovic
Author-email: aerkalov@gmail.com
